snippet: A bystander who was shot in the head on Thursday during clashes between Turkish police and protesters has died from his wounds, a hospital official told Reuters....

headline.print_headline: Turkish Bystander Dies After Being Shot in Head During Protest
headline.main: Turkish Bystander Dies After Being Shot in Head During Protest

lead_paragraph: A bystander who was shot in the head on Thursday during clashes between Turkish police and protesters has died from his wounds, a hospital official told Reuters.
